               <msContents class="#CM">
                  <summary><p>The palm-leaf bundle, a composite manuscript, contains:</p>
<list rend="numbered">

                     <item>The <title xml:lang="ta">Rāmatēvar Pūcāviti</title>, "Rules for worship by Rāmatēvar", which appears to be a manual for worship by Rāmatēvar, in 200 stanzas. The text is complete.</item>
                     <item>The <title xml:lang="ta">Nāṟkaraṇavupatēcam</title>, "Teaching on the four <emph rend="italic">karaṇam</emph>s", which appears to be a lesson on the four <emph rend="italic">karaṇam</emph>s, that is, the four organs of perceptions. The text is complete.</item>
  </list>
                  </summary>
                  
                  
